# copra

Copra - A static type stub generator for cocotb testbenches. 

> [Copra](https://www.britannica.com/topic/copra) is the kernel of the fruit of the coconut palm. 

Just like copra is the kernel of the fruit of the coconut palm, copra is the valuable typing information of the cocotb testbench.

## Overview

copra generates Python type stubs for cocotb testbenches, enabling better IDE support and static type checking.

## Features

- Auto-discovers DUT hierarchy
- Generates PEP 561-compliant stub files
- Supports all cocotb handle types
- Integrates with mypy and other type checkers

## Installation

```bash
pip install copra
```

## Quick Start

```bash
copra my_design
```

